column5: happened last night or this morning in Delhi ont licon mig welder   220v weld pac 155 2 brand new fold down boat seats grey with blue and white stripe (bought on Saterday) 1/5th scale rc car this is all custome and real eye catcher if you see it call police
That`s tough luck man, wouldn`t ya just love to be waiting in a dark corner with bat for the prick!

I'm going to say 100% they knew you or know someone who knows you... Random steal and not worth the charge for what they took... I mean if they stole your jewelry and flat screen TV it could be anyone... But an RC car, welder, and some boat seats?  Sorry about your luck.. I guess its not worth the insurance deductible?

Sounds more like stuff one might keep in their Garage, which is easier to access than say a house where one would keep jewelry and a flat screen. So it still sounds like a random garage hopping job, check kjiji and craigslist next few weeks for the RC car is about your best bet...
skinny I,m not to far from you I will keep my eye's peeled !
anyone seen any good deals on fold down boat seats

sounds like punks just checking doors here is a tip i learned a few years back after it happened to a house up the street. Ever forgot to lock your car your with remote for your garage door clipped on the sunvisor its a easy way to get into a garage, i keeep mine in a different place i can bet my truck and van are checked on a regular bases by kids looking for a quick score.
